# HAML

```
@haml
%div
  %h1 title
  %ul
    - %w{ cat dog pig bunny}.each do |animal|
      %li
        .container--picture{ class: animal }
          .picture--cover
            %a.link{:href => ""}
              %h1 Show more #{animal}
```
@css:

h1 {
 width: 100%;
 font-weight: bold;
 text-align: center;
 text-transform: uppercase;
}
ul, li {
display: inline-block;
}
.container--picture {
  width: 250px;
  height: 175px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow:
  inset 0 0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,0.6),
  0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  transition: all 0.4s ease-in-out;
}
.cat {
  background-image:   url(http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/511d104a69bedd1f7c000012/grumpy-cat-definitely-did-not-make-100-million.jpg);
  //background-image:   url(http://lsg-editor.herokuapp.com/assets/images/cat.jpg);
}
.pig {
  background-image: url(http://sp3.fotolog.com/photo/35/31/75/punkyluna/1320790798668_f.jpg);
}
.dog {
  background-image: url(http://30.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_lqgsins4RV1qd97mjo1_500.jpg);
}
.bunny {
  background-image: url(http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_OzamuWHmXBg/SQbSfKBzPwI/AAAAAAAAAMk/JhcS3gdGyX0/s400/conejo-bebe.jpg);
}
.cat, .dog, .pig, .bunny {
  background-size: cover;
}
.cat:hover, .dog:hover, .pig:hover {
  box-shadow:
  inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1),
  0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
.picture--cover {
  background: rgba(112, 122, 153, 0.6);
  width: inherit;
  height: inherit;
  overflow: hidden;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: all 0.4s ease-in-out;
  transform: scale(0);
}
.container--picture:hover .picture--cover {
   transform: scale(1);
   opacity: 1;
}
a.link{
color: white;
text-decoration: none;
font-weight: bold;
text-align: center;
text-transform: uppercase;
}
.lsg--button {
  background-color: #eafdf8;
  background-size: 60%;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 0;
  fill: white;
}
.lsg--code-block {
 background:#2EF1BD;
